sunday lovers is a 1980 internationally co-produced romantic comedy film directed by bryan forbes , gene wilder , dino risi and edouard molinaro .   it starred roger moore , gene wilder , priscilla barnes , lynn redgrave , denholm elliott and kathleen quinlan .   it is split into four segments , each from a different country ( england , france , usa and italy ) .   the film is notable for its use of sepia tones and slow wide angle shots to build a sense of impending dread .   it was released in italy in october 1980 and in america in early 1981 by metro-goldwyn-mayer and united artists .